{"tid":1335754,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我是一個想突破低薪嘅QA狗","createTime":"2019-07-20T16:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T16:20:43.000Z","uid":278788,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d31c36c28dfbdf71807495732224446453a45e3f","tid":1335754,"uid":278788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"大家好，想喺呢度呻一呻。首先介紹下小弟嘅背景. 巴打從21歲就一直做類似admin同data entry嘅職位。做咗足足六年一直都好憎做呢一行，本來以為就會係咁做一世，覺得好無奈又冇信心轉job。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩舊年10月公司又想請人做測試(QA)，開左internal application。肥佬左大學final year嘅我，希望擺在我眼前我梗係直刻申請。in完咁啱竟然又被我成功入左調左去入IT team。不過都冇咩出奇，我撞彩嘅原因都係因為我熟識公司嘅software。雖然呢9個月做左一段時間學曉左啲skill，例如，manual testing, selenium , basic SQL, agile methodology。但係我其實覺得自己嘅進展仲係慢得很。由於我地QA隊伍都係成立不久, 所以公司冇乜QA training。<br />\n<br />\n薪水暫時就係25k英磅，我唔想一世做一個junior QA。點樣先可以突破呢個位？？27歲的我miss左咁多機會，我唔知道點先可以追得上其他同齡同職巴絲嘅level。今日我求其網上查40k嘅要求成個人呆曬，都唔知點可以爬上去。係咪一定要學編程？望求高手多多指教。講嚟講去我都唔係好清楚自己想噏乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。點都好，分享左都算舒緩左感情。Thanks for reading.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪住....呢個post應該係發喺學術台定係上班台??? <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 如果我中文怪怪地，請見諒。我係英國大㗎(no I'm not a 鬼佬)。打左咁多中文都幾攰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.(Believe it or not, it took me ~30 minutes?) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想搵同行嘅人有時傾下計！@tgBada (不過有時差，slow reply）若有IT狗嘅tg gp, 請介紹 (or we can make one?)。"},{"pid":"75dccf74e5f4da3f7a3879c52b4fcbfb67934ea3","tid":1335754,"uid":96453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"25k 英鎊?  qa director ?"},{"pid":"6fc05d1724d85a5369fc5ed98072739eb3b5a17f","tid":1335754,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75dccf74e5f4da3f7a3879c52b4fcbfb67934ea3","tid":1335754,"uid":96453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"25k 英鎊?  qa director ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"係咪年薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2961a37765c450828e97e9db340c74141fbf8e65","tid":1335754,"uid":278788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75dccf74e5f4da3f7a3879c52b4fcbfb67934ea3","tid":1335754,"uid":96453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"25k 英鎊?  qa director ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"唔係。我只係一個qa tester, 我地冇qa lead. 隨左我仲有兩個人做qa. we have 6 developers including a lead developer."},{"pid":"26423df84447b0f04c66c8b8ce91e2c2594c4cc8","tid":1335754,"uid":278788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6fc05d1724d85a5369fc5ed98072739eb3b5a17f","tid":1335754,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75dccf74e5f4da3f7a3879c52b4fcbfb67934ea3","tid":1335754,"uid":96453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"25k 英鎊?  qa director ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"係咪年薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我應該寫清楚啲"},{"pid":"23c85cc371f381457b3cd93e6f6c182965e7532d","tid":1335754,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"其實 好多 job req 都係純粹 list 晒 所有 skills 出黎<br />\n因為好多 hr 都唔知要乜<br />\n所以你識裡面部分既話都ok"},{"pid":"f89e75ea872ea12527eb964ee48a96c58c8f59d7","tid":1335754,"uid":90609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:20:43.000Z","msg":"做QA 搵唔到食"}]}